1. Write an script which returns factorial fucntion of a number.

2. Write an script which checks if a number is prime.

3. Write an script which returns all words started with a spesific letter (for example a) and ended with another spesific letter from a given text file.

4. Write an script which finds and replaces "word 1" with "word 2" in a text file.

5. Write an script which draws and saves a plot from a given two columns file.
